# Session progress log

> append-only, maintained by session-start / session-end.
> When retention thresholds are exceeded, session-end delegates to memory-maintenance as the sole archive owner; keep the last complete session block.
> Archived sessions are indexed in memory/index.json (maintained by memory-maintenance) for session-start discovery.
> First use: copy this file to .harness/memory/progress.md.

